The paper introduces a new reinforcement learning algorithm that focuses on learning a simple dynamics model and efficient planning with strategic exploration. This makes it likely to fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer vision (cs.CV).
